==發行==
在美國，[[相對論傳媒|相對論傳媒]]原本將該片排於2015年10月30日上映<ref>{{cite web |last=Ge |first=Linda |url=http://www.thewrap.com/nicholas-hoult-and-felicity-jones-autobahn-gets-fall-release-date/ |title=Nicholas Hoult and Felicity Jones' 'Autobahn' Gets Fall Release Date |publisher=Thewrap.com |date=2015-02-04 |accessdate=2016-08-03 |archive-date=2020-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319000247/https://www.thewrap.com/nicholas-hoult-and-felicity-jones-autobahn-gets-fall-release-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，當相對論傳媒申請破產後，製片商該片重新出售版權<ref>{{cite web |last=Jaafar |first=Ali |url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/nicholas-hoult-autobahn-collide-eran-creevy-felicity-jones-im-global-42-ben-pugh-rory-aitken-1201490376/ |title=Eran Creevy’s ‘Collide’ Out Of Relativity; New Domestic Deal Imminent |publisher=Deadline |date= |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2020-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201019165016/https://deadline.com/2015/08/nicholas-hoult-autobahn-collide-eran-creevy-felicity-jones-im-global-42-ben-pugh-rory-aitken-1201490376/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2015年9月，宣布[[開路影業|開路影業]]已獲得該片的美國發行權<ref>{{cite web |author=Matthew Belloni |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/relativity-reveals-first-proposed-movie-827456 |title=Relativity Reveals First Proposed Movie Sale in Bankruptcy: Thriller 'Collide' |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |date=2015-09-26 |accessdate=2015-10-20 |archive-date=2018-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621143429/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/thr-esq/relativity-reveals-first-proposed-movie-827456 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年10月，開路影業將該片定於2016年4月1日上映<ref>{{cite web |last=Jaafar |first=Ali |url=http://deadline.com/2015/10/nicholas-hoult-felicity-jones-collide-im-global-open-road-anthony-hopkins-ben-kingsley-1201585039/ |title=Eran Creevy’s ‘Collide Movie Acquired By Open Road Films |publisher=Deadline |date=2015-10-16 |accessdate=2015-10-20 |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111174449/https://deadline.com/2015/10/nicholas-hoult-felicity-jones-collide-im-global-open-road-anthony-hopkins-ben-kingsley-1201585039/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來延期至2016年8月19日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/collide-trailer-video-felicity-jones-nicholas-hoult-1201762060/|title=‘Collide’ Trailer: Felicity Jones & Nicholas Hoult Rev Engines For August Bow|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-05-24|accessdate=2016-05-24|archive-date=2018-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180813014218/https://deadline.com/2016/05/collide-trailer-video-felicity-jones-nicholas-hoult-1201762060/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月，電影又被延至2017年2月3日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/collide-felicity-jones-nicholas-hoult-open-road-1201828525/|title=Felicity Jones-Nicholas Hoult Vehicle ‘Collide’ Back On Track For Winter 2017|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002030550/http://deadline.com/2016/09/collide-felicity-jones-nicholas-hoult-open-road-1201828525/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月，電影的美國上映日又改至2017年2月24日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movie/collide-2017#/slide/1|title=Collide|website=[[ComingSoon.net|ComingSoon.net]]|accessdate=2017-01-03|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401003415/https://www.comingsoon.net/movie/collide-2017#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於21條評論，新鮮度19%，平均得分4.2／10<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/collide_2017 |title=Collide (2017) |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango]] |accessdate=2017-02-24 |archive-date=2017-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128065117/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/collide_2017/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得39分，代表「普遍不佳」的評價<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/collide |title=Collide reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2017-02-23 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402203315/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/collide |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的反應在A+至F間落於「C+」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=CinemaScore |work=cinemascore.com |accessdate=2020-12-18 |archive-date=2019-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210223808/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，《偷天劫車手》與《[[逃出絕命鎮|逃出絕命鎮]]》、《[[搖滾藏獒|搖滾藏獒]]》共同上映競爭，預估能從兩千零四十五間戲院中獲得300萬至400萬美元的票房<ref name=preview>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/get-out-1201940270/ |title=Audiences Plan To Get Into ‘Get Out’ – Weekend B.O. Preview |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2017-02-22 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111224207/https://deadline.com/2017/02/get-out-1201940270/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國首週末票房收入僅150萬美元，位居當週第十三名，口碑不佳<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/get-out-collide-rock-dog-lego-batman-fifty-shades-darker-box-office-1201964096/ |title=Universal/Blumhouse’s ‘Get Out’ Now Grabbing A $30M+ Opening |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |accessdate=2017-02-27 |archive-date=2018-06-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/get-out-collide-rock-dog-lego-batman-fifty-shades-darker-box-office-1201964096/&date=2018-06-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

